name: INVITE
template:
INVITE sip:<<destination:string>> SIP/2.0
Via: SIP/2.0/UDP <<source_ip:string>>:<<source_port:integer>>
From: <<caller:string>>
To: <<callee:string>>
Call-ID: <<call_id:string>>
CSeq: <<cseq:integer>> INVITE
Max-Forwards: 70
Content-Length: 0
regex:
INVITE\ sip:(.*?)\ SIP/2\.0\\
Via:\ SIP/2\.0/UDP\ (.*?):(.*?)\\
From:\ (.*?)\\
To:\ (.*?)\\
Call\-ID:\ (.*?)\\
CSeq:\ (.*?)\ INVITE\\
Max\-Forwards:\ 70\\
Content\-Length:\ 0\\
\\
